name: @aritect/atomic
description: Aritect design system for building consistent, scalable interfaces.
author: Alexander Shelepenok <alxshelepenok@gmail.com>

scripts.build: bun run clean && bun run generate:exports && vite build --config internal/vite/vite-config.ts
